#: ../../utils/logger.rst:8
msgid "Using a Logger"
msgstr "使用 Logger"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:10
msgid ""
"Spinning Up ships with basic logging tools, implemented in the classes "
"`Logger`_ and `EpochLogger`_. The Logger class contains most of the basic"
" functionality for saving diagnostics, hyperparameter configurations, the"
" state of a training run, and the trained model. The EpochLogger class "
"adds a thin layer on top of that to make it easy to track the average, "
"standard deviation, min, and max value of a diagnostic over each epoch "
"and across MPI workers."
msgstr ""
"Spinning Up 內建了基本的日誌記錄工具，實作於 `Logger`_ 和 `EpochLogger`_ "
"這兩個類別中。Logger 類別包含了大部分基本功能，用於儲存診斷資訊、超參數"
"（hyperparameter）設定、訓練過程的狀態，以及訓練好的模型。EpochLogger 類別"
"在此基礎上增加了一層薄封裝，使得追蹤每個 epoch 以及跨 MPI worker 的診斷"
"值的平均值、標準差、最小值和最大值變得更加容易。"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:12 ../../utils/logger.rst:143
msgid "You Should Know"
msgstr "你應該知道"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:14
msgid "All Spinning Up algorithm implementations use an EpochLogger."
msgstr "所有 Spinning Up 的演算法實作都使用 EpochLogger。"

