#: ../../utils/logger.rst:37
msgid ""
"The ``store`` method is used to save all values of ``Test`` to the "
"``epoch_logger``'s internal state. Then, when ``log_tabular`` is called, "
"it computes the average, standard deviation, min, and max of ``Test`` "
"over all of the values in the internal state. The internal state is wiped"
" clean after the call to ``log_tabular`` (to prevent leakage into the "
"statistics at the next epoch). Finally, ``dump_tabular`` is called to "
"write the diagnostics to file and to stdout."
msgstr ""
"``store`` 方法用於將 ``Test`` 的所有值儲存到 ``epoch_logger`` 的內部狀態中。"
"接著，當呼叫 ``log_tabular`` 時，它會根據內部狀態中的所有值計算 ``Test`` "
"的平均值、標準差、最小值和最大值。內部狀態會在呼叫 ``log_tabular`` 後被清除"
"（以防止洩漏到下一個 epoch 的統計數據中）。最後，呼叫 ``dump_tabular`` "
"將診斷資訊寫入檔案和標準輸出。"

