#: ../../utils/logger.rst:132
msgid "Logging and PyTorch"
msgstr "日誌記錄與 PyTorch"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:134
msgid ""
"The preceding example was given in Tensorflow. For PyTorch, everything is"
" the same except for L42-43: instead of ``logger.setup_tf_saver``, you "
"would use ``logger.setup_pytorch_saver``, and you would pass it `a "
"PyTorch module`_ (the network you are training) as an argument."
msgstr ""
"前面的範例是使用 Tensorflow 撰寫的。對於 PyTorch，除了第 42-43 行之外一切相同："
"你需要使用 ``logger.setup_pytorch_saver`` 來替代 ``logger.setup_tf_saver``，"
"並將 `a PyTorch module`_（你正在訓練的網路）作為引數傳入。"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:136
msgid ""
"The behavior of ``logger.save_state`` is the same as in the Tensorflow "
"case: each time it is called, it'll save the latest version of the "
"PyTorch module."
msgstr ""
"``logger.save_state`` 的行為與 Tensorflow 的情況相同：每次呼叫時，"
"它都會儲存最新版本的 PyTorch module。"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:141
msgid "Logging and MPI"
msgstr "日誌記錄與 MPI"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:145
msgid ""
"Several algorithms in RL are easily parallelized by using MPI to average "
"gradients and/or other key quantities. The Spinning Up loggers are "
"designed to be well-behaved when using MPI: things will only get written "
"to stdout and to file from the process with rank 0. But information from "
"other processes isn't lost if you use the EpochLogger: everything which "
"is passed into EpochLogger via ``store``, regardless of which process "
"it's stored in, gets used to compute average/std/min/max values for a "
"diagnostic."
msgstr ""
"強化學習中有許多演算法可以透過 MPI 來對梯度（gradient）和／或其他關鍵量取平均值，"
"從而輕鬆實現並行化。Spinning Up 的 logger 設計為在使用 MPI 時能正常運作："
"只有 rank 0 的程序會寫入標準輸出和檔案。但如果你使用 EpochLogger，"
"來自其他程序的資訊不會遺失：無論儲存在哪個程序中，所有透過 ``store`` 傳入 "
"EpochLogger 的數據都會被用來計算診斷值的平均值／標準差／最小值／最大值。"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst:149
