msgstr "Logger 類別"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger:1
msgid "A general-purpose logger."
msgstr "通用日誌記錄器。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger:3
msgid ""
"Makes it easy to save diagnostics, hyperparameter configurations, the "
"state of a training run, and the trained model."
msgstr ""
"使儲存診斷資訊、超參數設定、訓練過程的狀態以及訓練好的模型變得容易。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.__init__:1
msgid "Initialize a Logger."
msgstr "初始化一個 Logger。"

#: ../../utils/logger.rst
msgid "Parameters"
msgstr "參數"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.__init__:3
msgid ""
"A directory for saving results to. If ``None``, defaults to a temp "
"directory of the form ``/tmp/experiments/somerandomnumber``."
msgstr ""
"儲存結果的目錄。如果為 ``None``，預設使用格式為 "
"``/tmp/experiments/somerandomnumber`` 的臨時目錄。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.__init__:7
msgid ""
"Name for the tab-separated-value file containing metrics logged "
"throughout a training run. Defaults to ``progress.txt``."
msgstr ""
"包含整個訓練過程中所記錄指標的 tab 分隔值檔案名稱。預設為 ``progress.txt``。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.__init__:11
msgid ""
"Experiment name. If you run multiple training runs and give them all the "
"same ``exp_name``, the plotter will know to group them. (Use case: if you"
" run the same hyperparameter configuration with multiple random seeds, "
"you should give them all the same ``exp_name``.)"
msgstr ""
"實驗名稱。如果你執行多次訓練並給它們相同的 ``exp_name``，繪圖工具會將它們"
"分為一組。（使用情境：如果你使用多個隨機種子執行相同的超參數設定，"
"應該給它們都設定相同的 ``exp_name``。）"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.dump_tabular:1
msgid "Write all of the diagnostics from the current iteration."
msgstr "寫出目前迭代的所有診斷資訊。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.dump_tabular:3
msgid "Writes both to stdout, and to the output file."
msgstr "同時寫入標準輸出和輸出檔案。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.log:1
msgid "Print a colorized message to stdout."
msgstr "將帶有顏色的訊息印到標準輸出。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.log_tabular:1
msgid "Log a value of some diagnostic."
msgstr "記錄某個診斷值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.log_tabular:3
msgid ""
"Call this only once for each diagnostic quantity, each iteration. After "
"using ``log_tabular`` to store values for each diagnostic, make sure to "
"call ``dump_tabular`` to write them out to file and stdout (otherwise "
"they will not get saved anywhere)."
msgstr ""
"每次迭代中，對每個診斷量只呼叫一次。使用 ``log_tabular`` 儲存每個診斷值後，"
"務必呼叫 ``dump_tabular`` 將它們寫入檔案和標準輸出（否則它們不會被儲存到任何地方）。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_config:1
msgid "Log an experiment configuration."
msgstr "記錄實驗設定。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_config:3
msgid ""
"Call this once at the top of your experiment, passing in all important "
"config vars as a dict. This will serialize the config to JSON, while "
"handling anything which can't be serialized in a graceful way (writing as"
" informative a string as possible)."
msgstr ""
"在實驗開始時呼叫一次，將所有重要的設定變數以 dict 傳入。這會將設定序列化為 "
"JSON，同時優雅地處理無法序列化的內容（盡可能寫出有意義的字串）。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_config:8
msgid "Example use:"
msgstr "使用範例："

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_state:1
msgid "Saves the state of an experiment."
msgstr "儲存實驗的狀態。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_state:3
msgid ""
"To be clear: this is about saving *state*, not logging diagnostics. All "
"diagnostic logging is separate from this function. This function will "
"save whatever is in ``state_dict``---usually just a copy of the "
"environment---and the most recent parameters for the model you previously"
" set up saving for with ``setup_tf_saver``."
msgstr ""
"需要澄清的是：這是關於儲存 *狀態*，而不是記錄診斷資訊。所有診斷日誌記錄與"
"此函式無關。此函式會儲存 ``state_dict`` 中的內容——通常只是環境的副本——"
"以及你先前透過 ``setup_tf_saver`` 設定儲存的模型的最新參數。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_state:9
msgid ""
"Call with any frequency you prefer. If you only want to maintain a single"
" state and overwrite it at each call with the most recent version, leave "
"``itr=None``. If you want to keep all of the states you save, provide "
"unique (increasing) values for 'itr'."
msgstr ""
"可以按你偏好的頻率呼叫。如果你只想維護單一狀態並在每次呼叫時用最新版本覆蓋，"
"請將 ``itr=None``。如果你想保留所有儲存的狀態，請為 'itr' 提供唯一的（遞增）值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_state:14
msgid ""
"Dictionary containing essential elements to describe the current state of"
" training."
msgstr "包含描述當前訓練狀態之必要元素的字典。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.save_state:17
msgid "An int, or None. Current iteration of training."
msgstr "一個整數或 None。目前的訓練迭代次數。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.setup_pytorch_saver:1
msgid "Set up easy model saving for a single PyTorch model."
msgstr "為單一 PyTorch 模型設定簡便的模型儲存功能。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.setup_pytorch_saver:3
msgid ""
"Because PyTorch saving and loading is especially painless, this is very "
"minimal; we just need references to whatever we would like to pickle. "
"This is integrated into the logger because the logger knows where the "
"user would like to save information about this training run."
msgstr ""
"由於 PyTorch 的儲存和載入特別簡單，這裡的實作非常精簡；我們只需要保留想要 "
"pickle 的物件的參考。這被整合到 logger 中，因為 logger 知道使用者想將此次"
"訓練的相關資訊儲存在哪裡。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.setup_pytorch_saver:9
msgid "Any PyTorch model or serializable object containing PyTorch models."
msgstr "任何 PyTorch 模型或包含 PyTorch 模型的可序列化物件。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.Logger.setup_tf_saver:1
msgid "Set up easy model saving for tensorflow (legacy TF1 support)."
msgstr "為 Tensorflow 設定簡便的模型儲存功能（舊版 TF1 支援）。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger:1
