msgstr "來記錄所需的值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.get_stats:1
msgid "Lets an algorithm ask the logger for mean/std/min/max of a diagnostic."
msgstr "讓演算法向 logger 查詢某個診斷值的平均值／標準差／最小值／最大值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.log_tabular:1
msgid "Log a value or possibly the mean/std/min/max values of a diagnostic."
msgstr "記錄一個值，或記錄某個診斷值的平均值／標準差／最小值／最大值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.log_tabular:3
msgid ""
"The name of the diagnostic. If you are logging a diagnostic whose state "
"has previously been saved with ``store``, the key here has to match the "
"key you used there."
msgstr ""
"診斷項目的名稱。如果你記錄的診斷項目先前已透過 ``store`` 儲存了狀態，"
"這裡的鍵必須與你在那裡使用的鍵一致。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.log_tabular:7
msgid ""
"A value for the diagnostic. If you have previously saved values for this "
"key via ``store``, do *not* provide a ``val`` here."
msgstr ""
