#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.log_tabular:10
msgid "If true, log min and max values of the diagnostic over the epoch."
msgstr "如果為 true，記錄該 epoch 中診斷值的最小值和最大值。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.log_tabular:13
msgid ""
"If true, do not log the standard deviation of the diagnostic over the "
"epoch."
msgstr "如果為 true，不記錄該 epoch 中診斷值的標準差。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.store:1
msgid "Save something into the epoch_logger's current state."
msgstr "將資料儲存到 epoch_logger 的目前狀態中。"

#: of spinup.utils.logx.EpochLogger.store:3
